If the container are the rain, they would rain from the cloud-- (docker registry)

Images are store in the docker registry

docker run nginx --> the real name of the image isnt nginx, but nginx/nginx.
When only one name is provided, we assume both name are equal.

image: user / image

where are the images:   docker hub

docker hub is a example of a docker registry, there are others

There are private registrys, that requires you to be logged in:  docker login